  <!-- OVERVIEW -->
  <section class="tang-section hor-fade">
    <h2>Overview</h2>
    <p>
      Park Tangerine is a vibrant expansion realm within the Ross Universe — a surreal, citrus‑infused world where
      clan colours, playful rituals, and mythic symbolism collide. It is the bright, joyful counterpoint to the
      heavier mythic arcs of Freedom, Everlight, and Clan Legacy.
    </p>
    <p>
      Though whimsical on the surface, Park Tangerine is built on emotional architecture and lineage logic — a place
      where characters explore identity, unity, and transformation through humour and colour.
    </p>
  </section>

  <!-- DISTRICTS -->
  <section class="tang-section hor-fade">
    <h2>Districts of Park Tangerine</h2>

    <div class="tang-districts">

      <div class="tang-district">
        <h3>The Citrus Grove</h3>
        <p>A glowing orchard where fruit carries emotional resonance and mythic properties.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="tang-district">
        <h3>The Zest Arena</h3>
        <p>A playful battleground for clan games, rituals, and chaotic competitions.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="tang-district">
        <h3>The Peel Market</h3>
        <p>A bustling bazaar of oddities, runes, snacks, and clan‑coded artefacts.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="tang-district">
        <h3>The Tangerine Falls</h3>
        <p>A shimmering waterfall of orange light — a place of reflection and emotional reset.</p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CHARACTERS -->
  <section class="tang-section hor-fade">
    <h2>Key Figures</h2>

    <div class="tang-characters">

      <div class="tang-character">
        <h3>The Zesty Keeper</h3>
        <p>Guardian of the grove. Speaks in riddles. Smells faintly of citrus.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="tang-character">
        <h3>The Peel Twins</h3>
        <p>Chaotic duo who run the Peel Market. Always hustling. Always arguing.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="tang-character">
        <h3>The Orange Runner</h3>
        <p>A mythic athlete who races through the Zest Arena leaving trails of light.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="tang-character">
        <h3>Z (Citrus Variant)</h3>
        <p>A playful, lighter version of Z — curious, bright, and emotionally open.</p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- RITUALS -->
  <section class="tang-section hor-fade">
    <h2>Rituals & Mythic Events</h2>

    <div class="tang-rituals">

      <div class="tang-ritual">
        <h3>The Great Peel Off</h3>
        <p>A chaotic clan competition involving speed, creativity, and citrus engineering.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="tang-ritual">
        <h3>The Zest Parade</h3>
        <p>A luminous procession celebrating unity, colour, and emotional expression.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="tang-ritual">
        <h3>The Orange Eclipse</h3>
        <p>A rare celestial event where the sky turns tangerine and runes glow.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="tang-ritual">
        <h3>The Unity Squeeze</h3>
        <p>A symbolic ritual where clans merge their citrus essences into harmony.</p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- VISUAL LANGUAGE -->
